about-me.description: Hello! My name is Victor, I'm a Front-End Developer and I love creating things. Since I was little I've always had a taste for technology but it wasn't until 2020 that I got the chance to start my path in programming, since then I don't plan to stop!

window.description: I love the JavaScript language and it's what I've been using since I started in this programming world, but I'm open to learn any stack whenever there is the opportunity.

projects.starwars-app: It is a simple Star Wars universe blog using the 'swapi' API that is still in process.
